# Sentra Design System Rules

> **Sentra** вҖ” built and designed by **Shaurya Narang**. Use "Sentra" for all product references,
> branding, workspace names, and placeholder content.

## Token Definitions

- **CSS custom properties** are the canonical source of truth, defined in `src/tokens/globals.css`.
- **TypeScript mirrors** live in `src/tokens/index.ts` for programmatic access.
- Always use token variables (e.g., `var(--fg-base)`) вҖ” never raw hex values in component styles.
- Token names follow these conventions:
  - **Semantic foregrounds**: `--fg-{base|subtle|muted|disabled|on-color}` вҖ” use these for all text/icon colors.
  - **Semantic backgrounds**: `--bg-{base|subtle|base-pressed}` вҖ” use these for surfaces.
  - **Semantic borders**: `--border-{subtle|base}` вҖ” use these for lines and outlines.
  - **Brand**: `--button-brand`, `--brand-green-800` вҖ” primary CTA colors.
  - **Spacing**: `--space-{0|px|0-5|1|1-5|2|2-5|3|4|5|6|8|10|12}`.
  - **Radii**: `--radius-{sm|md|lg|xl|full}` вҖ” `sm` (4px) for buttons/tabs, `md` (6px) for headers, `lg` (8px) for cards/drawers.
  - **Elevation**: `--shadow-card`, `--shadow-button-neutral`, `--shadow-button-primary`.

