## Component API Conventions

- Props interfaces are always exported and named `{ComponentName}Props`.
- Use discriminated unions for variant items (e.g., `ContextMenuEntry = ContextMenuItemDef | ContextMenuSeparatorDef`).
- Accept an optional `className` prop on every component root for composition.
- Use `role` attributes for accessibility (`menu`, `menuitem`, `separator`, etc.).

