|-------------|-------------------------------------------|
| width       | 240px max (contains stepper at 144px)     |
| item height | 26px per stepper item                     |
| padding     | `--space-6` (24px) all sides              |
| gap         | 2px between stepper items                 |
| active item | bold text + dot indicator on the left     |
| text        | 13px Inter Medium, `--fg-subtle`          |
| active text | 13px Inter Medium, `--fg-base`            |

