### Top Bar Convention

Every page has a **TopBar** (48px tall, white background) as the page header inside the floating card.

```css
.topBar {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: space-between;
  height: 48px;
  padding: 0 24px;       /* --space-6 */
  background: var(--bg-base);
  flex-shrink: 0;
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
}
```

#### TopBar Internal Structure

```
в”Ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”җ
в”Ӯ [Breadcrumb text] в”Ӯ [All] [Pending] [Resolved]   [Create] в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ     fg-subtle        tabs group                  button  в”Ӯ
в””в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҳ
```

**Left side** (flex, gap 12px):
1. **Breadcrumb** вҖ” page title in `fg-subtle` (#52525b), 13px medium.
2. **Vertical divider** вҖ” 1px wide, 16px tall, `border-subtle` (#efeff0).
3. **Tabs Group** вҖ” horizontal filter tabs (optional, page-dependent).

**Right side** (flex, justify-end):
1. **Primary action button** вҖ” usually "Create" (see Button spec below).

### Breadcrumb

Three variants depending on page type:

**Main page (single-level):**
- Just the page name as text.
- Text: `--fg-subtle` (#52525b), 13px medium.

**Sub page (multi-level with back):**
- Back icon button (24px, neutral, left chevron) + breadcrumb items separated by `>` chevron (12px).
- Parent item: `--fg-muted` (#71717a) вҖ” clickable, navigates back.
- Current item: `--fg-subtle` (#52525b) вҖ” not clickable.
- Chevron separator: 12Г—12px, `--fg-muted`.
- Gap between icon button and breadcrumb: 12px.
- Gap between breadcrumb items: 4px.

**Inner page (multi-level, no back):**
- Multi-level breadcrumb (Parent `>` Current) without a back icon button.
- Parent item: `--fg-muted` (#71717a) вҖ” clickable, navigates to parent list.
- Current item: `--fg-subtle` (#52525b) вҖ” not clickable.
- Same chevron and gap rules as Sub page.

### Tabs Group (within TopBar)

Used for filtering views (e.g., All / Pending / Resolved).

| State    | Background                | Text Color        | Shadow           |
|----------|---------------------------|-------------------|------------------|
| Active   | `--bg-base` (white)       | `--fg-base`       | `--shadow-card`  |
| Inactive | transparent               | `--fg-muted`      | none             |
| Hover    | transparent               | `--fg-subtle`     | none             |

- Height: 24px, padding: 10px horizontal, border-radius: `--radius-sm` (4px).
- Gap between tabs: 2px.
- Font: 13px medium.

### Dividers

Three divider types used throughout the product:

**Horizontal divider (`type=fill`)**:
- Between TopBar and Main body: use `border-bottom` on `.topBar` вҖ” **never** a separate `<div>`.
- Between content groups: 1px, `--border-subtle` (#efeff0).
- In overview panel footer sections: `--border-base` (#e4e4e7).

**Horizontal divider (`type=dots`)**:
- Used within the Overview panel to separate content groups.
- Rendered as a dotted border: `border-top: 1px dashed var(--border-subtle)`.
- Groups related metadata fields.

**Vertical divider (`type=fill`)**:
- Used to separate Inner body from Overview panel in sub pages.
- 1px wide, `--border-subtle` (#efeff0), full height of the content area.
- Rendered as a `<div>` with `width: 1px; background: var(--border-subtle)`.

