| Property    | Value                               |
|-------------|--------------------------------------|
| max-width   | 320px                               |
| background  | `--bg-subtle` (#fafafa)             |
| padding     | `--space-6` (24px) horiz, `--space-4` (16px) vert |
| item gap    | `--space-3` (12px) between rows     |

### Text Color Rules

| State     | Token           | Example           |
|-----------|-----------------|-------------------|
| Label     | `--fg-muted`    | "Source", "Filters" |
| Default   | `--fg-disabled` | "Not selected", "None applied", "n/a" |
| Filled    | `--fg-base`     | "Intercom", "18"  |

### Best Practices (from Figma spec)
- Group related contents and use `divider type=dots` to split sections.
- Preferably add an illustrative `avatar content=icon` to filled items.
- Do NOT add avatar before labels вҖ” avatars go on the value side only.
- Label column is fixed-width (120px), value column is flexible.
- Row gap within a group: horizontal `--space-1-5` (6px).

