### Column Types

Tables support these cell types:
- **Text** вҖ” plain label.
- **Badge** вҖ” small colored badge.
- **Status dot + label** вҖ” colored dot (8px) + text.
- **Avatar + name** вҖ” user avatar (24px) + name text.
- **Action menu** вҖ” "..." overflow button (rightmost column).

### Row Grouping

Tables can have collapsible group headers (triangle icon + group name). Groups are indented under their header.

### Pagination

- Shown below the table with a top border (`--border-subtle`).
- Contains page navigation and item count.

